          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Excitation  of isomer states  of nuclei near N = 82 is",
                " investigated. The   cross  sections  of  the  (g,n)-m",
                " reactions on Ba-138, Nd-142, and Sm-144 in the energy",
                " range 8  - 18 MeV are measured.  Energy dependence of",
                " isomeric yields  ratio   is   considered.   Essential",
                " reduction of  the isomeric ratios with N observed for",
                " the nuclei under  study  is  resulted  to  the  shell",
                " effects and semi-direct processes contribution."
              ]
            }
          ],
